title: China to sign more high-standard free trade agreements: Xi
description: China will negotiate and sign high-standard free trade agreements with more countries, Chinese President Xi Jinping said Friday. Xi made the remarks while delivering a keynote speech at the opening ceremony of the Second Belt and Road Forum for International Cooperation in Beijing. #BeltandRoad
